== 過往慈善活動 ==
在2015年，其中一間受惠機構「[[龍耳|龍耳]]」，該機構為聾人及其家人提供不同類型的綜合社會服務、醫學介入，並為他們舉辦親子工作坊以克服聾人及弱聽人士所帶來的溝通問題，一同建構共融社會<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/education-community/article/1892413/hong-kong-bankers-sing-their-hearts-out-good |title=Hong Kong bankers sing their hearts out for a good cause |publisher=[[南華早報|南華早報]] |date=2015-12-17 |accessdate=2015-12-18 |archive-date=2017-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170502034004/http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/education-community/article/1892413/hong-kong-bankers-sing-their-hearts-out-good |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

